      <description>&lt;p&gt;Do you aim to make information more accessible to everyone? I am looking for students to work on different tasks for text adaption (e.g. Text Simplification, Readability Assessment, etc.).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You could either apply to one of the School of Computer Science &lt;a href=&#34;https://findaphd.com/phds/project/natural-language-processing-for-text-adaptation/?p141418&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;studentships&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;strong&gt;Deadline 29/04&lt;/strong&gt;), or be &lt;a href=&#34;https://findaphd.com/phds/project/natural-language-processing-for-text-adaptation-self-funded-students-only/?p141424&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;self-funded&lt;/a&gt;.
Do not hesitate to get in touch if you&amp;rsquo;re interested!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
